        mounted() {
            this.initChart()
            /* this.__resizeHandler = debounce(() => {
                 if (this.chart) {
                     this.chart.resize()
                 }
             }, 100)
             window.addEventListener('resize', this.__resizeHandler)*/
        },
        beforeDestroy() {
            if (!this.chart) {
                return
            }
            // window.removeEventListener('resize', this.__resizeHandler)
            this.chart.dispose()
            this.chart = null
        },
        methods: {
            initChart() {
                this.chart = echarts.init(this.$el, 'macarons')

                this.chart.setOption({

                        series: {
                            type: 'sunburst',
                            highlightPolicy: 'ancestor',
                            data: this.datas,
                            radius: [0, '95%'],
                            sort: null,
                            levels: [{}, {
                                r0: '15%',
                                r: '35%',
                                itemStyle: {
                                    borderWidth: 2
                                },
                                label: {
                                    rotate: 'tangential'
                                }
                            }, {
                                r0: '35%',
                                r: '70%',
                                label: {
                                    align: 'right'
                                }
                            }, {
                                r0: '70%',
                                r: '72%',
                                label: {
                                    position: 'outside',
                                    padding: 3,
                                    silent: false
                                },
                                itemStyle: {
                                    borderWidth: 3
                                }
                            }]
                        },
                animationDuration: animationDuration
                })
            }
        }
    }
</script>
